Here is the sample Google Sheets template for this project: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1AxPXjI8jotr1aBvorLKt7fy2zCsrR9oPLrDkPGndDww/edit?usp=sharing 

The 3rd party SMS gateway I used for this project is Semaphore. To utilize the code, paste your unique API key and the current API URL of Semaphore (it changes from time to time depending on the version) or the API URL of any 3rd party SMS gateway.
